<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/global.css">
    <script src="/scripts/darkmode.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>

<!-- About Page Container -->
<div id="about-page" class="about-page">
    <!-- About Header -->
    <div id="about-header" class="section-header">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Food Ordering App, where we bring delicious meals right to your doorstep, making dining easy and convenient.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <div id="mission-section" class="section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is simple: to offer a seamless and fast food ordering service, bringing the best dishes right to your doorstep. We aim to deliver high-quality meals while ensuring customer satisfaction and convenience.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <div id="how-it-works-section" class="section">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Browse our extensive menu of delicious dishes.</li>
            <li>Add your favorites to your cart.</li>
            <li>Proceed to checkout and complete your order.</li>
            <li>Sit back, relax, and track your order in real-time as it gets delivered to you.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Features Section -->
    <div id="core-features-section" class="section">
        <h2>Core Features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Wide range of cuisine options.</li>
            <li>Easy-to-use interface for browsing the menu and placing orders.</li>
            <li>Real-time order tracking and delivery updates.</li>
            <li>Secure payment options for a hassle-free checkout.</li>
            <li>24/7 customer support to assist you whenever needed.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <div id="values-section" class="section">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <ul class="values-list">
            <li><strong>Quality</strong>: We ensure that every meal is made with the finest ingredients.</li>
            <li><strong>Convenience</strong>: Place your order from the comfort of your home, anytime, anywhere.</li>
            <li><strong>Customer Satisfaction</strong>: Your happiness is our priority. We strive to deliver excellent service every time.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <div id="team-section" class="section">
        <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
        <p>Our team consists of passionate food enthusiasts, talented chefs, and tech experts, all working together to bring you the best food delivery experience.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <div id="contact-section" class="section">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions, suggestions, or need assistance, feel free to reach out to us:</p>
        <ul class="contact-list">
            <li>Email: contact@foodordering.com</li>
            <li>Phone: +123-456-7890</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <div id="cta-section" class="section">
        <h2>Get Started Today!</h2>
        <p>Ready to indulge in delicious food? Download our app and place your first order today. We can't wait to serve you!</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>